新婚生活。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>分析文(含劇透)<br />\n《逃恥》：厭世地擁抱生命中的缺憾</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/59675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F59675&d=3XxoN59xZ6GKXDea4epuE8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=73e8551b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/59675</a><br />\n《逃恥》橫掃91回學院賞<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/h2TnKc2.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh2TnKc2.png&d=3XxoN59xZ6GKXDea4epuE8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=bb33dbf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/h2TnKc2.png</a>"},{"pid":"97936f0d76ed22ec9e97e010e686b64d82ea27a3","tid":146577,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"Close Post"},{"pid":"4502957c1fd419567239f8062ba92a83fb2eb7f3","tid":146577,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda8af18ad652751aa102d802a7e2917754d134a","tid":146577,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我仲mon娛樂台"},{"pid":"5355318ec8e2b45507a7012fd9301ec3f2d39081","tid":146577,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"呢排係咪興開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba80dffba10f3478bf0ada0e74d815d567dd9426","tid":146577,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}